    "sources": ["memory/workspace/experience-index.md", "scripts/write-experience.ps1", "scripts/recall-search.ps1", "manifest.json"],
    "mustContain": ["Experience Index", "write-experience.ps1", "experience-index.md"]
  },
  {
    "question": "如果我问你还记得我是什么样的人、我的偏好和经历吗，应该优先召回什么？",
    "sources": ["memory-policy.json", "scripts/recall-search.ps1", "scripts/write-memory.ps1", "README.md"],
